§7§oHere you can find explanations and tutorials on all of the ways of making infinite resources!

§fIt is clear that, in order to achieve my goals, I need to CREATE!
Luckily, there are a lot of ways of generating matter using science, magic, and a combination of both.
I will keep track of the various methods to generate matter 'ex nihilo' in this chapter.
betterquesting:10.name:8: I need more! A lot More!
